WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.166
Welcome to the heart of Paris

00:00:02.166 --> 00:00:04.333
where the authentic flavors of Tunisia

00:00:04.333 --> 00:00:06.500
meet the spirit of the city.

00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:08.666
We offer you the best of

00:00:08.666 --> 00:00:10.833
Tunisian cuisine, from couscous to lablabi,

00:00:10.833 --> 00:00:13.000
all prepared with love and rich

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:15.166
traditions. Every meal with us is

00:00:15.166 --> 00:00:17.333
a journey to Tunisia without leaving

00:00:17.333 --> 00:00:19.500
Paris. Come and join us at

00:00:19.500 --> 00:00:21.666
the table reserved just for you,

00:00:21.666 --> 00:00:23.833
and receive a warm welcome from

00:00:23.833 --> 00:00:26.000
the heart.

